FBIS4-5823 "dreas072_c_94011" FBIS-EAS-94-072 Daily Report 14 Apr 1994 North Korea Kim Il-song Sends Funds to Koreans in Japan Kim Il-song Sends Funds to Koreans in Japan SK1404104594 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1025 GMT 14 Apr 94 SK1404104594 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, April 14 (KCNA) -- The great leader President Kim Il-song sent again a large sum of educational aid fund and stipends amounting to 104.8 million yen in Japanese currency for the democratic national education of Koreans in Japan. Educational aid fund and stipends sent by him in 127 installments amounts to 42,012,992,433 yen.
